s that investors interested in trading its shares from the us should use a broker that has trading and registration arrangements in canada or otherwise trade through us subsidiaries of canadian banks join our mailing list email address    enter the code shown above  information for us shareholders holding their positions through dtc follow us on home  projects  investors  community  disclaimer  privacy  contact copyright ® largo resources ltd designed by tmxequicom and powered by q inc  largo resources ltd  investors  stock chart  quote menu portuguese contact stock chart historical stock quote stock chart historical stock quote stock quote stock quote tse lgoca previous close  change   change  intraday high  intraday low  price  volume   week high   week low  todays open  jul    pm pricing delayed  minutes stock quote stock quote otc lgorf previous close  change   change  intraday high  intraday low  price  volume   week high   week low  todays open  july    am pricing delayed  minutes join our mailing list email address    enter the code shown above  follow us on home  projects  investors  community  disclaimer  privacy  contact copyright ® largo resources ltd designed by tmxequicom and powered by q inc  largo resources ltd  projects  overview menu portuguese contact maracás  maracás menchen mine more photos  videos check out our latest pictures watch our last videos more campo alegre more currais novos more northern dancer more download thumb download description   maracas  preliminary economic assessment  mb   maracas  resource estimate  mb   maracas  feasibility studymaps  mb join our mailing list email address    enter the code shown above  follow us on home  projects  investors  community  disclaimer  privacy  contact copyright ® largo resources ltd designed by tmxequicom and powered by q inc  largo resources ltd  disclaimer menu portuguese contact disclaimer largo makes no representation that the information contained in this website or your access to it is 