racás menchen mine and generating cashflows it presents a unique opportunity for investors to gain exposure to the vanadium market flagship maracás menchen mine world’s premier vanadium mine highest grade quality lowest cost production commenced august  glencore offtake  takeorpay contract for  years experienced management with expertise in vanadium strong investor base capitalizing on market demand and supply instability in strategic metals pipeline of projects in place for growth more currais novos tungsten project located in brazil reprocessing of tailings to produce tungsten concentrate initial production commenced in  project on careandmaintenance due to drought more northern dancer project located in yukon canada with direct access to alaska highway large tungsten and molybdenum deposit open pit mining process preliminary economic assessment completed in  more campo alegre project located in bahia brazil exploration stage project large potentially worldclass iron vanadium and titanium deposit historical noncompliant resource more mr robert campbell vice president of exploration to largo and a qualified person as defined by ni   has reviewed and approved this information downloads view all first quarter financial statements pdf  kb first quarter mda pdf  kb latest blog april   largo resources celebrates canadas th anniversary june   announcing graduation to tsx march   join us at pdac  join our mailing list email address    enter the code shown above  follow us on home  projects  investors  community  disclaimer  privacy  contact copyright ® largo resources ltd designed by tmxequicom and powered by q inc  largo resources ltd  about us  company profile menu portuguese contact company profile lgotsx  otcqblgorflargo resources ltd is a growing strategic mineral company with projects in brazil and canada largo is presently focused on the production of vanadium at its maracás menchen mine investment highlights largo resources ltd tsxlgo otcqblgorf is a midtier minin